metadata.name: MXKING
metadata.description:
MXKING are one of the most powerful species living in meadow and grasslands. They are nocturnal creatures who leading alien species living and operating at meadows and grasslands. MXKING make chemical reaction inside their bodies that allows them to light up with which they alert each other and speak with the language similar to Morse code, in addition, the top part of their head or crown is inflated so they levitate to outer space at night.
 body length: 2 to 3 cm 
crown size: 5 to 10 cm 
operate at middle and press hands grasslands
